      "weather": "FINE",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STAINED ACES (2) has missed the frame at his last two but did run well three back when third (16.90) in a Grade 5 at Q Straight. Better than last run and makes appeal this time. GOLDSTAR HECTOR (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (20.03) in a Grade 5 at this track. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from six attempts. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. TIGGY BOODIE (6) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 2.5 lengths at Q Straight in a handy 19.34 beating Venomous Miss. Expecting another bold showing. MALIPANO BEACH (7) looks a top-three hope after a break.",
